{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109156516849-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109156516849-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100124910276-1","P_10100124910276-2","P_10100124910276-3","P_10100124910276-4","P_10100124910276-5","P_10100124910276-6","P_10100124910276-7","P_10100124910276-8"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":540,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>郑板桥爱子</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">郑板桥不仅是清朝有名的画家、诗人、书法家，而且是深深懂得家教的教育家。他非常讲究“爱子之道”。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">郑板桥在外任职时，曾将他6岁的儿子小宝留在乡下，由他的弟弟郑默代为抚养，郑默对小宝十分宠爱。小宝常炫耀道：“我爹在外面做大官！”有时小宝还欺侮人家的孩子，这些事让郑板桥知道了，心里非常焦急，就给弟弟写信道：<strong>“我52岁才生一个儿子，哪有不爱的道理？</strong>但教更重于养。”他要求弟弟对孩子严加管教。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当郑板桥病危时，他把儿子叫到床前，突然提出要吃儿子做的馒头，待儿子将慢头送到父亲病床前时，父亲已经断了气。小宝悲痛地大哭，忽然发现旁边有张纸条，上面写道：“流自己的汗，吃自己的饭，自己的事情自己干，靠天靠人靠祖宗，不算是好汉。”郑板桥临终前给儿子上了“自立”的一课。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>给加线字选择正确读音。</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">朝</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">向</span></p>","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100047615188","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":["KPF_10100000004118"]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000623083","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"cháo","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"zhāo","file":{"file